366class BattleExperienceEvent : public BasicEvent
367{
368public:
369 static uint32 const ExperiencedSpells[5];
370 static uint32 const ExperiencedTimes[5];
371
372 BattleExperienceEvent(Creature* creature) : _creature(creature), _level(0) { }
373
374 bool Execute(uint64 timer, uint32 /*diff*/) override
375 {
376 if (!_creature->IsAlive())
377 return true;
378
379 _creature->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(ExperiencedSpells[_level]);
380 ++_level;
381
382 _creature->CastSpell(_creature, ExperiencedSpells[_level], true);
383 if (_level < (_creature->GetMap()->IsHeroic() ? 4 : 3))
384 {
385 _creature->m_Events.AddEvent(this, timer + ExperiencedTimes[_level]);
386 return false;
387 }
388
389 return true;
390 }
391
392private:
393 Creature* _creature;
394 int32 _level;
395};

400class PassengerController
401{
402public:
403 PassengerController()
404 {
405 ResetSlots(TEAM_HORDE, nullptr);
406 }
407
408 void ResetSlots(TeamId teamId, MotionTransport* t)
409 {
410 _transport = t;
411
412 for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_SLOTS; ++i)
413 {
414 _controlledSlots[i].Clear();
415 _respawnCooldowns[i] = time_t(0);
416 }
417
418 _spawnPoint = teamId == TEAM_HORDE ? &OrgrimsHammerAddsSpawnPos : &SkybreakerAddsSpawnPos;
419 _slotInfo = teamId == TEAM_HORDE ? OrgrimsHammerSlotInfo : SkybreakerSlotInfo;
420 }
421
422 bool SummonCreatures(Creature* summoner, PassengerSlots first, PassengerSlots last)
423 {
424 if (!_transport)
425 return false;
426
427 bool summoned = false;
428 time_t now = GameTime::GetGameTime().count();
429 for (int32 i = first; i <= last; ++i)
430 {
431 if (_respawnCooldowns[i] > now)
432 continue;
433
434 if (_controlledSlots[i])
435 {
436 Creature* current = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*_transport, _controlledSlots[i]);
437 if (current && current->IsAlive())
438 continue;
439 }
440
441 Position spawnPos = SelectSpawnPoint();
442 if (Creature* passenger = summoner->SummonCreature(_slotInfo[i].Entry, spawnPos, TEMPSUMMON_CORPSE_TIMED_DESPAWN, 15000))
443 {
444 if (!passenger->GetTransport())
445 _transport->AddPassenger(passenger, true);
446 passenger->ApplySpellImmune(0, IMMUNITY_ID, 49576, true); // death grip
447
448 if (i >= SLOT_MAGE_1 && i <= SLOT_MORTAR_4) // only these npcs are pooled
449 {
450 _controlledSlots[i] = passenger->GetGUID();
451 _respawnCooldowns[i] = time_t(0);
452 }
453 passenger->AI()->SetData(ACTION_SET_SLOT, i);
454 summoned = true;
455 }
456 }
457
458 return summoned;
459 }
460
461 void ClearSlot(PassengerSlots slot)
462 {
463 _controlledSlots[slot].Clear();
464 _respawnCooldowns[slot] = GameTime::GetGameTime().count() + _slotInfo[slot].Cooldown;
465 }
466
467private:
468 Position SelectSpawnPoint() const
469 {
470 float angle = frand(-M_PI * 0.5f, M_PI * 0.5f);
471 Position newPos;
472 newPos.m_positionX = _spawnPoint->GetPositionX() + 2.0f * std::cos(angle);
473 newPos.m_positionY = _spawnPoint->GetPositionY() + 2.0f * std::sin(angle);
474 newPos.m_positionZ = _spawnPoint->GetPositionZ();
475 newPos.SetOrientation(_spawnPoint->GetOrientation());
476 _transport->CalculatePassengerPosition(newPos.m_positionX, newPos.m_positionY, newPos.m_positionZ, &(newPos.m_orientation));
477 return newPos;
478 }
479
480 ObjectGuid _controlledSlots[MAX_SLOTS];
481 time_t _respawnCooldowns[MAX_SLOTS];
482 MotionTransport* _transport;
483 Position const* _spawnPoint;
484 SlotInfo const* _slotInfo;
485};

487class DelayedMovementEvent : public BasicEvent
488{
489public:
490 DelayedMovementEvent(Creature* owner, Position const& dest) : _owner(owner), _dest(dest) { }
491
492 bool Execute(uint64, uint32) override
493 {
494 if (!_owner->IsAlive() || !_owner->GetTransport())
495 return true;
496
497 float x, y, z, o;
498 _dest.GetPosition(x, y, z, o);
499 _owner->GetTransport()->CalculatePassengerPosition(x, y, z, &o);
500 _owner->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(EVENT_CHARGE_PREPATH, x, y, z, false);
501 return true;
502 }
503
504private:
505 Creature* _owner;
506 Position const& _dest;
507};

509class ResetEncounterEvent : public BasicEvent
510{
511public:
512 ResetEncounterEvent(Unit* caster, uint32 spellId, ObjectGuid otherTransport) : _caster(caster), _spellId(spellId), _otherTransport(otherTransport) { }
513
514 bool Execute(uint64, uint32) override
515 {
516 _caster->CastSpell(_caster, _spellId, true);
517 _caster->GetTransport()->ToMotionTransport()->UnloadNonStaticPassengers();
518 _caster->GetTransport()->AddObjectToRemoveList();
519
520 if (Transport* transport = ObjectAccessor::GetTransport(*_caster, _otherTransport))
521 {
522 transport->ToMotionTransport()->UnloadNonStaticPassengers();
523 transport->AddObjectToRemoveList();
524 }
525
526 return true;
527 }
528
529private:
530 Unit* _caster;
531 uint32 _spellId;
532 ObjectGuid _otherTransport;
533};

535class npc_gunship : public CreatureScript
536{
537public:
538 npc_gunship() : CreatureScript("npc_gunship") { }
539
540 struct npc_gunshipAI : public NullCreatureAI
541 {
542 npc_gunshipAI(Creature* creature) : NullCreatureAI(creature), _instance(creature->GetInstanceScript()), _teamIdInInstance(TeamId(creature->GetInstanceScript()->GetData(DATA_TEAMID_IN_INSTANCE))), _died(false), _summonedFirstMage(false)
543 {
544 me->SetRegeneratingHealth(false);
545 }
546
547 void DamageTaken(Unit*, uint32& damage, DamageEffectType, SpellSchoolMask) override
548 {
549 if (_instance->GetBossState(DATA_ICECROWN_GUNSHIP_BATTLE) != IN_PROGRESS)
550 {
551 damage = 0;
552 return;
553 }
554
555 if (damage >= me->GetHealth())
556 {
557 JustDied(nullptr);
558 damage = me->GetHealth() - 1;
559 return;
560 }
561
562 if (_summonedFirstMage)
563 return;
564
565 if (me->GetTransport()->GetEntry() != uint32(_teamIdInInstance == TEAM_HORDE ? GO_THE_SKYBREAKER_H : GO_ORGRIMS_HAMMER_A))
566 return;
567
568 if (!me->HealthBelowPctDamaged(90, damage))
569 return;

572 if (Creature* captain = me->FindNearestCreature(_teamIdInInstance == TEAM_HORDE ? NPC_IGB_MURADIN_BRONZEBEARD : NPC_IGB_HIGH_OVERLORD_SAURFANG, 200.0f))
573 captain->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_SPAWN_MAGE);

576 void JustDied(Unit* /*killer*/) override
577 {
578 if (_died || _instance->GetBossState(DATA_ICECROWN_GUNSHIP_BATTLE) != IN_PROGRESS)
579 return;
580 _died = true;
581
582 bool isVictory = me->GetTransport()->GetEntry() == GO_THE_SKYBREAKER_H || me->GetTransport()->GetEntry() == GO_ORGRIMS_HAMMER_A;
583 _instance->SetBossState(DATA_ICECROWN_GUNSHIP_BATTLE, isVictory ? DONE : FAIL);
584 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_ICECROWN_CITADEL, 0);
585
586 if (Creature* creature = me->FindNearestCreature(me->GetEntry() == NPC_ORGRIMS_HAMMER ? NPC_THE_SKYBREAKER : NPC_ORGRIMS_HAMMER, 200.0f))
587 {
588 _instance->SendEncounterUnit(ENCOUNTER_FRAME_DISENGAGE, creature);
589 if (Aura* a = creature->GetAura(SPELL_CHECK_FOR_PLAYERS))
590 a->SetDuration(0);
591 }
592 _instance->SendEncounterUnit(ENCOUNTER_FRAME_DISENGAGE, me);
593 if (Aura* a = me->GetAura(SPELL_CHECK_FOR_PLAYERS))
594 a->SetDuration(0);
595
596 uint32 explosionSpell = isVictory ? SPELL_EXPLOSION_VICTORY : SPELL_EXPLOSION_WIPE;
597 if (MotionTransport* t = (me->GetTransport() ? me->GetTransport()->ToMotionTransport() : nullptr))
598 {
599 Transport::PassengerSet const& passengers = t->GetStaticPassengers();
600 for (Transport::PassengerSet::const_iterator itr = passengers.begin(); itr != passengers.end(); ++itr)
601 {
602 if ((*itr)->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_UNIT || (*itr)->GetEntry() != NPC_GUNSHIP_HULL)
603 continue;
604 (*itr)->ToCreature()->CastSpell((*itr)->ToCreature(), explosionSpell, true);
605 }
606 }
607
608 uint32 cannonEntry = _teamIdInInstance == TEAM_HORDE ? NPC_HORDE_GUNSHIP_CANNON : NPC_ALLIANCE_GUNSHIP_CANNON;
609 if (GameObject* go = _instance->instance->GetGameObject(_instance->GetGuidData(DATA_ICECROWN_GUNSHIP_BATTLE)))
610 if (MotionTransport* t = go->ToMotionTransport())
611 {
612 Transport::PassengerSet const& passengers = t->GetStaticPassengers();
613 for (Transport::PassengerSet::const_iterator itr = passengers.begin(); itr != passengers.end(); ++itr)
614 {
615 if ((*itr)->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_UNIT || (*itr)->GetEntry() != cannonEntry)
616 continue;
617 Creature* cannon = (*itr)->ToCreature();
618 cannon->CastSpell(cannon, SPELL_EJECT_ALL_PASSENGERS, true);
619
620 WorldPacket data(SMSG_PLAYER_VEHICLE_DATA, cannon->GetPackGUID().size() + 4);
621 data << cannon->GetPackGUID();
622 data << uint32(0);
623 cannon->SendMessageToSet(&data, true);
624
625 cannon->RemoveVehicleKit();
626 }
627 }
628
629 uint32 creatureEntry = NPC_IGB_MURADIN_BRONZEBEARD;
630 uint8 textId = isVictory ? SAY_MURADIN_VICTORY : SAY_MURADIN_WIPE;
631 if (_teamIdInInstance == TEAM_HORDE)
632 {
633 creatureEntry = NPC_IGB_HIGH_OVERLORD_SAURFANG;
634 textId = isVictory ? SAY_SAURFANG_VICTORY : SAY_SAURFANG_WIPE;
635 }
636 if (Creature* creature = me->FindNearestCreature(creatureEntry, 200.0f))
637 creature->AI()->Talk(textId);
638
639 if (isVictory)
640 {
641 if (Transport * transport = _instance->instance->GetTransport(_instance->GetGuidData(DATA_ICECROWN_GUNSHIP_BATTLE)))
642 if (MotionTransport* otherTransport = transport->ToMotionTransport())
643 otherTransport->EnableMovement(true);
644
645 me->GetTransport()->ToMotionTransport()->EnableMovement(true);
646
647 if (Creature* ship = me->FindNearestCreature(_teamIdInInstance == TEAM_HORDE ? NPC_ORGRIMS_HAMMER : NPC_THE_SKYBREAKER, 200.0f))
648 {
649 ship->CastSpell(ship, SPELL_TELEPORT_PLAYERS_ON_VICTORY, true);
650 ship->CastSpell(ship, SPELL_ACHIEVEMENT, true);
651 ship->CastSpell(ship, SPELL_AWARD_REPUTATION_BOSS_KILL, true);
652 }
653
654 for (uint8 i = 0; i < 2; ++i)
655 if (GameObject* go = _instance->instance->GetGameObject(_instance->GetGuidData(i == 0 ? DATA_ICECROWN_GUNSHIP_BATTLE : DATA_ENEMY_GUNSHIP)))
656 if (MotionTransport* t = go->ToMotionTransport())
657 {
658 Transport::PassengerSet const& passengers = t->GetPassengers();
659 for (Transport::PassengerSet::const_iterator itr = passengers.begin(); itr != passengers.end(); ++itr)
660 {
661 if ((*itr)->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_UNIT)
662 continue;
663 Creature* c = (*itr)->ToCreature();
664 if (c->GetEntry() == NPC_SKYBREAKER_MARINE || c->GetEntry() == NPC_SKYBREAKER_SERGEANT || c->GetEntry() == NPC_KOR_KRON_REAVER || c->GetEntry() == NPC_KOR_KRON_SERGEANT)
665 c->DespawnOrUnsummon(1);
666 }
667 }
668 }
669 else
670 {
671 uint32 teleportSpellId = _teamIdInInstance == TEAM_HORDE ? SPELL_TELEPORT_PLAYERS_ON_RESET_H : SPELL_TELEPORT_PLAYERS_ON_RESET_A;
672 me->m_Events.AddEvent(new ResetEncounterEvent(me, teleportSpellId, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_ENEMY_GUNSHIP)), me->m_Events.CalculateTime(8000));
673 }
674 }
675
676 void SetGUID(ObjectGuid guid, int32 id/* = 0*/) override
677 {
678 if (id != ACTION_SHIP_VISITS_ENEMY && id != ACTION_SHIP_VISITS_SELF)
679 return;
680
681 std::map<ObjectGuid, uint32>::iterator itr = _shipVisits.find(guid);
682 if (itr == _shipVisits.end())
683 {
684 if (id == ACTION_SHIP_VISITS_ENEMY)
685 _shipVisits[guid] = ACTION_SHIP_VISITS_ENEMY;
686 }
687 else if (itr->second) // if 0 then achiev already failed
688 {
689 if (id == ACTION_SHIP_VISITS_SELF)
690 {
691 if (itr->second == ACTION_SHIP_VISITS_ENEMY)
692 itr->second = ACTION_SHIP_VISITS_SELF;
693 else if (itr->second == ACTION_SHIP_VISITS_ENEMY_2)
694 itr->second = ACTION_SHIP_VISITS_SELF_2;
695 }
696 else
697 {
698 if (itr->second == ACTION_SHIP_VISITS_SELF)
699 {
700 if (me->GetMap()->Is25ManRaid())
701 itr->second = 0;
702 else
703 itr->second = ACTION_SHIP_VISITS_ENEMY_2;
704 }
705 else if (itr->second == ACTION_SHIP_VISITS_SELF_2)
706 itr->second = 0;
707 }
708 }
709 }
710
711 uint32 GetData(uint32 id) const override
712 {
713 if (id != ACTION_SHIP_VISITS_ENEMY)
714 return 0;
715
716 for (std::map<ObjectGuid, uint32>::const_iterator itr = _shipVisits.begin(); itr != _shipVisits.end(); ++itr)
717 if (itr->second == 0)
718 return 0;
719
720 return 1;
721 }

725 TeamId _teamIdInInstance;
726 std::map<ObjectGuid, uint32> _shipVisits;
727 bool _died;
728 bool _summonedFirstMage;
729 };

876 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
877 {
878 if (_instance->GetBossState(DATA_ICECROWN_GUNSHIP_BATTLE) == IN_PROGRESS)
879 {
880 if (me->GetVictim())
881 {
882 if (me->GetMotionMaster()->GetCurrentMovementGeneratorType() == CHASE_MOTION_TYPE)
883 {
884 if (me->GetVictim()->GetPositionZ() >= 478.0f)
885 {
886 float x, y, z, o;
887 me->GetHomePosition(x, y, z, o);
888 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(0, x, y, z, false);
889 }
890 }
891 else
892 {
893 if (me->GetVictim()->GetPositionZ() < 478.0f)
894 me->GetMotionMaster()->MoveChase(me->GetVictim());
895 }
896 }
897
898 if (checkTimer <= diff)
899 {
900 checkTimer = 1000;
901 Map::PlayerList const& pl = me->GetMap()->GetPlayers();
902 for (Map::PlayerList::const_iterator itr = pl.begin(); itr != pl.end(); ++itr)
903 if (Player* p = itr->GetSource())
904 if (CanAIAttack(p) && me->IsValidAttackTarget(p))
905 {
906 me->SetInCombatWith(p);
907 p->SetInCombatWith(me);
908 me->AddThreat(p, 0.0f);
909 }
910 }
911 else
912 checkTimer -= diff;
913 }
914
915 UpdateVictim();
916 _events.Update(diff);
917
918 switch (_events.ExecuteEvent())
919 {
920 case 0:
921 break;
922 case EVENT_INTRO_H_1:
923 Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_1);
924 break;
925 case EVENT_INTRO_H_2:
926 Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_2);
927 break;
928 case EVENT_INTRO_SUMMON_SKYBREAKER:
929 sTransportMgr->CreateTransport(GO_THE_SKYBREAKER_H, 0, me->GetMap());
930 break;
931 case EVENT_INTRO_H_3:
932 Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_3);
933 break;
934 case EVENT_INTRO_H_4:
935 Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_4);
936 break;
937 case EVENT_INTRO_H_5:
938 if (Creature* muradin = me->FindNearestCreature(NPC_IGB_MURADIN_BRONZEBEARD, 200.0f))
939 muradin->AI()->Talk(SAY_MURADIN_INTRO_H);
940 break;
941 case EVENT_INTRO_H_6:
942 Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_6);
943 break;
944 case EVENT_KEEP_PLAYER_IN_COMBAT:
945 if (_instance->GetBossState(DATA_ICECROWN_GUNSHIP_BATTLE) == IN_PROGRESS)
946 {
947 //_instance->DoCastSpellOnPlayers(SPELL_LOCK_PLAYERS_AND_TAP_CHEST);

949 for (Map::PlayerList::const_iterator itr = pl.begin(); itr != pl.end(); ++itr)

954 }
955 break;
956
957 case EVENT_SUMMON_MAGE:
958 Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_MAGES);
959 _controller.SummonCreatures(me, SLOT_FREEZE_MAGE, SLOT_FREEZE_MAGE);
960 break;
961 case EVENT_ADDS:
962 Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_ENTER_SKYBREAKER);
963 _controller.SummonCreatures(me, SLOT_MAGE_1, SLOT_MAGE_2);
964 _controller.SummonCreatures(me, SLOT_MARINE_1, Is25ManRaid() ? SLOT_MARINE_4 : SLOT_MARINE_2);
965 _controller.SummonCreatures(me, SLOT_SERGEANT_1, Is25ManRaid() ? SLOT_SERGEANT_2 : SLOT_SERGEANT_1);

972 }

975 if (MotionTransport* skybreaker = transport->ToMotionTransport())
976 {
977 float x, y, z, o;
978 SkybreakerTeleportExit.GetPosition(x, y, z, o);
979 skybreaker->CalculatePassengerPosition(x, y, z, &o);
980 me->SummonCreature(NPC_TELEPORT_EXIT, x, y, z, o, TEMPSUMMON_TIMED_DESPAWN, 23000);
981 }

983 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_ADDS_BOARD_YELL, 6000);
984 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_ADDS, 60000);

986 case EVENT_ADDS_BOARD_YELL:
987 if (Creature* muradin = me->FindNearestCreature(NPC_IGB_MURADIN_BRONZEBEARD, 200.0f))
988 muradin->AI()->Talk(SAY_MURADIN_BOARD);
989 break;
990 case EVENT_CHECK_RIFLEMAN:
991 if (_controller.SummonCreatures(me, SLOT_RIFLEMAN_1, Is25ManRaid() ? SLOT_RIFLEMAN_8 : SLOT_RIFLEMAN_4))
992 {
993 if (_axethrowersYellCooldown < GameTime::GetGameTime().count())

995 Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_AXETHROWERS);
996 _axethrowersYellCooldown = GameTime::GetGameTime().count() + 5;
997 }
998 }
999 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_CHECK_RIFLEMAN, 1500);
1000 break;
1001 case EVENT_CHECK_MORTAR:
1002 if (_controller.SummonCreatures(me, SLOT_MORTAR_1, Is25ManRaid() ? SLOT_MORTAR_4 : SLOT_MORTAR_2))
1003 {
1004 if (_rocketeersYellCooldown < GameTime::GetGameTime().count())
1005 {
1006 Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_ROCKETEERS);
1007 _rocketeersYellCooldown = GameTime::GetGameTime().count() + 5;

1009 }
1010 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_CHECK_MORTAR, 1500);

1012 case EVENT_CLEAVE:
1013 if (me->GetVictim())

1016 break;
1017
1018 default:
1019 break;
1020 }
1021
1022 if (!me->GetVictim() || me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING))
1023 return;
1024
1025 if (me->IsWithinMeleeRange(me->GetVictim()))
1026 DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
1027 else if (me->isAttackReady())
1028 {
1029 me->SetOrientation(me->GetAngle(me->GetVictim()));
1030 me->CastSpell(me->GetVictim(), SPELL_RENDING_THROW, false);
1031 me->resetAttackTimer();
1032 }
1033 }

1130 {
1131 if (action == ACTION_ENEMY_GUNSHIP_TALK)

1149 skybreaker->CastSpell(skybreaker, SPELL_CHECK_FOR_PLAYERS, true);

1151 }
1152 else if (action == ACTION_SPAWN_MAGE)
1153 {
1154 time_t now = GameTime::GetGameTime().count();
1155 if (_firstMageCooldown > now)
1156 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_MAGE, (_firstMageCooldown - now) * IN_MILLISECONDS);
1157 else
1158 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_MAGE, 1);
1159 }
1160 else if (action == ACTION_SPAWN_ALL_ADDS)
1161 {
1162 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_ADDS, 12000);
1163 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_CHECK_RIFLEMAN, 13000);
1164 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_CHECK_MORTAR, 13000);
1165 if (Is25ManRaid())
1166 _controller.SummonCreatures(me, SLOT_MAGE_1, SLOT_MORTAR_4);
1167 else
1168 {
1169 _controller.SummonCreatures(me, SLOT_MAGE_1, SLOT_MAGE_2);
1170 _controller.SummonCreatures(me, SLOT_MORTAR_1, SLOT_MORTAR_2);
1171 _controller.SummonCreatures(me, SLOT_RIFLEMAN_1, SLOT_RIFLEMAN_4);
1172 }
1173 }
1174 else if (action == ACTION_EXIT_SHIP)
1175 {
1176 G3D::Vector3 points[MuradinExitPathSize];
1177 for (uint8 i = 0; i < MuradinExitPathSize; ++i)
1178 {
1179 points[i].x = MuradinExitPath[i].GetPositionX();
1180 points[i].y = MuradinExitPath[i].GetPositionY();
1181 points[i].z = MuradinExitPath[i].GetPositionZ();
1182 }
1183 Movement::PointsArray path(points, points + MuradinExitPathSize);
1184 me->SetWalk(true);
1185 Movement::MoveSplineInit init(me);
1186 init.DisableTransportPathTransformations();
1187 init.MovebyPath(path, 0);
1188 init.Launch();
1189 me->DespawnOrUnsummon(18000);
1190 }
1191 }

1665 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_WOUNDING_STRIKE, urand(5000, 10000));
1666 }

1668 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
1669 {
1670 if (Instance->GetBossState(DATA_ICECROWN_GUNSHIP_BATTLE) != IN_PROGRESS)
1671 return;
1672 if (me->GetReactState() == REACT_PASSIVE)
1673 return;
1674 npc_gunship_boarding_addAI::UpdateAI(diff);
1675 _events.Update(diff);
1676 UpdateVictim();
1677 if (me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING) || me->HasAura(SPELL_BLADESTORM))
1678 return;
1679 if (!anyValid)
1680 {
1681 TriggerBurningPitch(me);
1682 return;
1683 }
1684 if (!me->GetVictim())
1685 return;
1686 switch (_events.ExecuteEvent())
1687 {
1688 case 0:
1689 break;
1690 case EVENT_BLADESTORM:
1691 me->CastSpell(me->GetVictim(), SPELL_BLADESTORM, false);
1692 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_BLADESTORM, urand(25000, 30000));
1693 break;
1694 case EVENT_WOUNDING_STRIKE:
1695 me->CastSpell(me->GetVictim(), SPELL_WOUNDING_STRIKE, false);
1696 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_WOUNDING_STRIKE, urand(7000, 13000));
1697 break;
1698 default:
1699 break;
1700 }
1701 DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
1702 }
1703
1704 private:
1705 EventMap _events;
1706 };

1886 }
